OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1775127597
OL,3,CNon-crime hate incidents scrapped five
OL,4,Cmonths after Met stops investigating
OL,6,FNon-crime hate incidents will
OL,7,Fofficially be scrapped five months
OL,8,Fafter the Metropolitan Police
OL,9,Fannounced it would stop investigating
OL,10,Fthem.
OL,12,FUnder current rules, police forces are
OL,13,Fexpected to look into acts which
OL,14,Fappear to be motivated by hostility
OL,15,Ftowards people with certain
OL,16,Fcharacteristics including race,
OL,17,Freligion, disability or gender, that
OL,18,Ffall short of being crimes.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
