OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1775127597
OL,3,CNon-crime hate incidents scrapped five
OL,4,Cmonths after Met stops investigating
OL,6,FUnclear guidance has led to officers
OL,7,Fbeing called to people's homes over
OL,8,F"insults and routine arguments", the
OL,9,FGovernment said.
OL,11,FLondon's Met Police last year
OL,12,Fannounced it would no longer
OL,13,Finvestigate the incidents after it
OL,14,Fdropped a probe into social media
OL,15,Fposts about transgender issues by
OL,16,FFather Ted creator Graham Linehan.
OL,18,FThere will be no automatic wiping of
OL,19,Fthe incidents from people's records
OL,20,Fafter the decision, it is reported.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@_O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/13
