CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1775127597
OL,3,CNon-crime hate incidents scrapped five
OL,4,Cmonths after Met stops investigating
OL,6,FScrapping non-crime hate incidents
OL,7,Fwill give officers more time to focus
OL,8,Fon their day-to-day policing,
OL,9,Fministers hope.
OL,11,FThe move, which comes after a College
OL,12,Fof Policing and National Police
OL,13,FChiefs' Council review, will see a
OL,14,Ftighter definition of what constitutes
OL,15,Fan incident requiring police
OL,16,Finvolvement.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1775127597
OL,3,CNon-crime hate incidents scrapped five
OL,4,Cmonths after Met stops investigating
OL,6,FFewer reports will automatically
OL,7,Ftrigger a police record under the
OL,8,Fplans, with officers and call handlers
OL,9,Frecording information only where there
OL,10,Fis a clear risk of harm.
OL,12,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood said:
OL,13,F"Under these reforms, forces will no
OL,14,Flonger be policing perfectly legal
OL,15,Ftweets.
OL,17,F"Instead, they will be doing what they
OL,18,Fdo best: patrolling our streets,
OL,19,Fcatching criminals, and keeping
OL,20,Fcommunities safe."
OL,26,@uD@AOUyD@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1775127597
OL,3,CNon-crime hate incidents scrapped five
OL,4,Cmonths after Met stops investigating
OL,6,FBut responding to the announcement,
OL,7,Fshadow home secretary Chris Philp said
OL,8,Fthe policy would make no difference to
OL,9,Fpolice time.
OL,11,F"This is simply a rebrand of non-crime
OL,12,Fhate incidents with a more restrictive
OL,13,Ftriage process," he said.
OL,15,F"Reports are still logged, personal
OL,16,Fdata still recorded, and disclosure
OL,17,Frules are unchanged. Officers and
OL,18,Fstaff will still be tied up monitoring
OL,19,Fincidents that do not meet the
OL,20,Fcriminal threshold, at a cost in time
OL,21,Fand resources.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@PO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1775127597
OL,3,CNon-crime hate incidents scrapped five
OL,4,Cmonths after Met stops investigating
OL,6,F"People want the police focused on
OL,7,Fcatching criminals and keeping streets
OL,8,Fsafe. Conservatives have been
OL,9,Fconsistently clear the police should
OL,10,Fget back to basics and non-crime hate
OL,11,Fincidents should be scrapped to free
OL,12,Fup police time."
OL,14,FNon-crime hate incidents were
OL,15,Fintroduced after the murder of Stephen
OL,16,FLawrence in 1993 and an inquiry into
OL,17,Fhis death, setting up a system for
OL,18,Freporting and recording racist
OL,19,Fincidents and crimes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@PO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1775127597
OL,3,CNon-crime hate incidents scrapped five
OL,4,Cmonths after Met stops investigating
OL,6,FDuring a Lords debate earlier this
OL,7,Fmonth, his mother, Labour peer
OL,8,FBaroness Doreen Lawrence of Clarendon
OL,9,Fsaid insults can lead to violence.
OL,11,FShe urged peers to consider "what
OL,12,Fimplication" abandoning the system
OL,13,Fcould have.
OL,15,F"It depends on how you see non-crime
OL,16,Fhate and it depends on who's at the
OL,17,Freceiving end of that," she said.
OL,19,F"Now for me, it led to the murder of
OL,20,Fmy son.
OL,26,@sD@]OUtD@LO]wD@AOUyD@WO]{D@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1775127597
OL,3,CNon-crime hate incidents scrapped five
OL,4,Cmonths after Met stops investigating
OL,6,F"Now, individuals who think they've
OL,7,Fgot the right to walk around and talk
OL,8,Fabout, especially, young black men in
OL,9,Fa certain way, what starts off as just
OL,10,Fverbal, it leads to violence."
OL,12,FShe added: "How do you move forward if
OL,13,Fit moves from verbal into violence and
OL,14,Fyou have no way of tracking back where
OL,15,Fit started from?"
OL,17,FStephen's father Neville Lawrence said
OL,18,Fthe decision was going back on Lord
OL,19,FMacpherson's inquiry following his
OL,20,Fson's death.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@^O]tD@LOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/13
