CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1775127597
OL,3,CNon-crime hate incidents scrapped five
OL,4,Cmonths after Met stops investigating
OL,6,FHe told the Daily Mirror: "A lot of
OL,7,Fpeople are going to get really angry
OL,8,Fand maybe turn to violence. There are
OL,9,Fsupposed to be laws to make sure
OL,10,Fpeople can live decent lives.
OL,12,F"If the police aren't going to record
OL,13,Fthese incidents then who are?"
OL,15,FIrish comedy writer Linehan was
OL,16,Farrested at Heathrow Airport last year
OL,17,Fon suspicion of inciting violence over
OL,18,Fthree posts he had made on X.
OL,26,@nD@[OUtD@AOUuD@^O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/13
