PN,40610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1775127597
OL,3,CNon-crime hate incidents scrapped five
OL,4,Cmonths after Met stops investigating
OL,6,FHis arrest sparked debate, with
OL,7,FConservative politicians and Harry
OL,8,FPotter author JK Rowling among those
OL,9,Fvoicing their outrage.
OL,11,FFollowing Linehan's arrest, Met Police
OL,12,FCommissioner Sir Mark Rowley said
OL,13,Fofficers were in "an impossible
OL,14,Fposition" when dealing with statements
OL,15,Fmade online.
OL,26,@uD@ROUvD@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/13
