PN,40611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1775127597
OL,3,CNon-crime hate incidents scrapped five
OL,4,Cmonths after Met stops investigating
OL,6,FSpeaking about the Home Secretary's
OL,7,Fmove, Assistant Chief Constable Tom
OL,8,FHarding, director at the College of
OL,9,FPolicing, said: "Non-crime hate
OL,10,Fincidents are being replaced with a
OL,11,Fsystem that better serves both the
OL,12,Fpublic and modern-day policing.
OL,14,F"We have clearly established the
OL,15,Fcurrent approach does not meet the
OL,16,Fexpectations of either.
OL,26,@qD@QOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
