OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1775127597
OL,3,CNon-crime hate incidents scrapped five
OL,4,Cmonths after Met stops investigating
OL,6,F"Today we are setting out a
OL,7,Ffundamentally different way of
OL,8,Fhandling reports so that officers can
OL,9,Ffocus efforts on their core duties of
OL,10,Fpreventing crime and protecting
OL,11,Fcommunities, while making clear that
OL,12,Flawful free speech is not a police
OL,13,Fmatter.
OL,15,F"Recording of non-crime hate incidents
OL,16,Frepresents a very small proportion of
OL,17,Foverall police demand and while well
OL,18,Fintentioned, there has been a
OL,19,Fdisproportionate use of the process
OL,20,Fwhich has eroded public trust."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/13
